vote.title: A public hearing to receive comments on (1) re-adopting and continuing in effect Chapter 12, "City Youth Program Standards of Care," of the Dallas City Code, to re-establish standards of care for certain city youth programs in compliance with state law; and, (2) at the close of the public hearing; approving of an ordinance to re-adopt Chapter 12 of the Dallas City Code -  Financing: No cost consideration to the City
